  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I only apologize to them [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] that I tried to-- to represent them and their horror, and tell to the world [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] what I personally-- what all of them went through, and those horrifying years.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "From the Death March?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The Death March was-- and I'm glad you asked me this.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I had a double fight with me.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I have seen it that the end is close.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We could hear, you know, artillery and the airplanes.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We saw that the end is coming.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Was-- there were-- the Germans, himself, have seen.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They start to get panicky, but the day of reckoning will come.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I said to myself that I am losing it.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] My own preservation to be able to make it to the last, because the Germans said, shall we lose the war, five minutes before 12, you will also perish.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But that was actually their main purpose.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I was feeling it that mine end is also coming because I saw there is so many left and right, and horrifying things, thousands in felling it on the sides of the roads.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I said, 'I'm not going to make it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I feel I'm not going to make it.' [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] Somehow, somewhere, my blessed mother's face, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] and my grandfather, and some of the others-- I saw my mother's face, kept on saying, 'You have to make it.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "You have to make it.' And I was bitterly crying.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I said, 'I can't anymore.' Many time I fell and I picked myself up and I kept on going.",
      "word_count": 19
    }
  ],
